OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine possible in the far
OL,7,Feast this evening. Otherwise rain will
OL,8,Fspread across the region overnight,
OL,9,Faccompanied by blustery winds,
OL,10,Fparticularly along exposed coasts and
OL,11,Fhigh ground. A milder night than of
OL,12,Flate.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FAny lingering rain in the
OL,15,Feast quickly clearing, leaving a
OL,16,Fblustery day with a mix of sunshine
OL,17,Fand showers. The showers will be heavy
OL,18,Fand possibly thundery, before easing
OL,19,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
