OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FFurther showers likely on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fbefore turning drier, brighter and
OL,8,Fwarmer on Thursday. Mostly sunny and
OL,9,Fvery warm on Friday with perhaps the
OL,10,Fodd shower developing later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
